{"tid":2362882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"茶/茶葉有冇可以發酵成酒?","createTime":"2021-01-11T18:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T19:10:55.000Z","uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f53058e558f429797afd96be7276efe286b963d","tid":2362882,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"突然諗點解冇茶味嘅酒<br />\n如有請介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99825c5b84b4b6968807a5aad1fe25a1d910bb90","tid":2362882,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:50:43.000Z","msg":"Chartreuse"},{"pid":"1c329bd8951dd304cb7c152aaf8dc2a43e6c9a4f","tid":2362882,"uid":28245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"茶走"},{"pid":"5e5d677e8dc9e101ee69373e881908d1737cb181","tid":2362882,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c329bd8951dd304cb7c152aaf8dc2a43e6c9a4f","tid":2362882,"uid":28245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"茶走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615ccf0449f94b2009d9c394a5e8b8f9c92a2de1","tid":2362882,"uid":61005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:58:05.000Z","msg":"因為茶是故鄉濃<br />\n酒是故鄉醇"},{"pid":"384320cd9071239832f26487f060d3a152adce8d","tid":2362882,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為以前啲人興以茶代酒，所以茶樓=酒樓"},{"pid":"ff7dc3a45c09474bb26b3464102a0d646f43c5e1","tid":2362882,"uid":244137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n因為茶葉本身冇糖份，發酵唔到酒精<br />\n而且茶葉有茶多酚抗菌，酵母點做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想飲茶味酒咪自己溝<br />\nchoya都有支宇治茶梅酒不過好難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1362a8bedc9adc61b8bc800c99c957b9f7f721c8","tid":2362882,"uid":57148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T19:10:55.000Z","msg":"有茶味既酒一向都有<br />\ne.g: <a href=\"https://www.absolut.com/us/absolutcollaborations/absolut-wild-tea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.absolut.com%2Fus%2Fabsolutcollaborations%2Fabsolut-wild-tea%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Bcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=213d4baa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.absolut.com/us/absolutcollaborations/absolut-wild-tea/</a><br />\n<br />\n發酵既都有, 可以自己整:<br />\n<a href=\"https://delishably.com/beverages/Recipe-How-to-make-Wine-from-Tea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdelishably.com%2Fbeverages%2FRecipe-How-to-make-Wine-from-Tea&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Bcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c3a8e9c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://delishably.com/beverages/Recipe-How-to-make-Wine-from-Tea</a><br />\n只係茶本身無咩野可以促進發酵過程 佢只係提供味道 你要加糖<br />\n<br />\nKombucha都係發酵過既茶 不過酒精含量好低 你當係酸既jolly sandy"}]}